hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm self-employed perfect lip nutrients balmoney Just as all things now seem to be decided by committee, from primetime comedy shows to privatising the NHS, it is actually a committee that makes the call on which of the growing number of ‘disgraced’ prominent people with honours get to keep their titles, and which gets ‘stripped’, to use the correct term – ‘stripped’, like ‘traipse’ has very specific uses in English – you are stripped of your title and your dignity, but that’s mostly it, like you ‘traipse round the shops’, or ‘traipse through the house with muddy boots on’, but at any other time, traipsing does not seem to occur.
